				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">hi. i have a lev 35 bard and i was seal hunting deep in DF when an enemy realm toke ocntrol of DF. i died my the hands of a monster and my grave is stuck in DF. =( i know it realy doesnt matter as most of u are thinking, but this can get quite anouying if its always happening to u. (getting into big grps and going deep into dungeons, then sum idiot pulls the wrong mob and u all die).
<br />

<br />
if this happens u are then unable to get ur grave and ur xp back which u worked hard for. so i have a small suggestion around this situation.
<br />

<br />
I suggest that a Church be built in each of the main citys. i.e. tir na nog and camelot and what ever the mid 1 is called =). in this church there would be a magnificent looking statue at the alter and if u select this statue and type /pray it imitates the same as praying at ur grave, without the bother of trying to get past lots of agro and dieing again!  
<br />

<br />
i think this idea might work well because it wont make things to easy because u gota travel to the city to get it, and also it will  make things alot better for those people who get themselves in these situations. it will also make the realms more magnificent looking and not to mention the fact that its the dark ages where people belive in spirits and gods and stuff but yet there is no very kool looking temples. (well not in tir na nog anyway)
<br />

<br />
this could also be a place with healers and grovey looking spell casters hanging around (all npc's of course).
<br />

<br />
thanx for reading this. i hope u take up the idea.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
