				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I like your idea of a statue or church/temple to pray at. How many times I've died somewhere that is next to impossible to get back to? Tons. Bottoms on dungeons, epic zones and so forth. Plus the times when I couldn't find my grave at all! 
<br />

<br />
Perhaps you would have to pay a special fee to the priests for the service. I always hoped they would have had in game maps where your grave would be marked so you could navigate but that wont happen.
<br />

<br />
I thought another idea might be to buy a special scroll from the church in your capital that you carried with you. This scroll would magically alert you when you are near your grave, perhaps giving a message like:
<br />

<br />
"You sense your grave to the NE"
<br />

<br />
I dunno, perhaps its a small thing to be asking for when so many classes in this game still have issues and balancing issues. Oh well, good idea though.
<br />

<br />
Sprie Littlebottom
<br />
46 LW Keen Champ of Guinevere
<br />
Nocturnal</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
